| hmget        | hmget key field1 field2...fieldN        |                                        | O(1)   |                                                                        |
| hmset        | hmset key field1 value1...fieldN valueN |                                        | O(1)   |                                                                        |
| hincrby      | hincrby key field count                 |                                        | O(1)   |                                                                        |
| hgetall      | hgetall key                             | 返回hash key对应所有的field**和**value | O(n)   |                                                                        |
